    <item>
      <title>美国经济在选举前放缓但稳健</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/us-economy-slowing-but-solid-near-election-unemployment-low</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统大选前夕，最近的数据显示，获胜者将继承一个蓬勃发展的经济，这得益于美国消费者尽管多年来物价和利率居高不下，但仍坚持消费。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/us-economy-slowing-but-solid-near-election-unemployment-low</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 19:49:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
