    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚总统蒂努布不顾各州反对，坚持税制改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/nigeria-s-president-bola-tinubu-doubles-down-on-rejected-tax-reform-bills</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚总统博拉·蒂努布不会撤回已提交给议员的四项税收法案，此举可能会激怒各州有权有势的州长，因为他们的支持对于拟议的改革的实施至关重要。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/nigeria-s-president-bola-tinubu-doubles-down-on-rejected-tax-reform-bills</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 18:03:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
